@startuml
title State Machine: Officer Status

[*] --> OffDuty
OffDuty : Not scheduled\nAvailable for call

OffDuty --> OnDuty : Shift starts
OnDuty : Scheduled shift\nPatrol/desk duty

OnDuty --> Available : Ready for calls
Available : In service\nAwaiting assignments

Available --> Dispatched : Receives call
Dispatched : Assigned to incident\nEn route

Dispatched --> OnScene : Arrives at location
OnScene : At incident location\nHandling situation

OnScene --> InPursuit : Suspect flees
InPursuit : Actively pursuing\nHigh risk

InPursuit --> Arresting : Apprehends suspect
Arresting : Making arrest\nSecuring scene

Arresting --> Transporting : Moving suspect
Transporting : To station/jail\nIn vehicle

Transporting --> ReportWriting : After transport
ReportWriting : Documenting incident\nFiling reports

ReportWriting --> Available : Reports complete
OnScene --> Available : Incident resolved
Transporting --> Available : Handoff complete

InPursuit --> Emergency : Officer needs help
Emergency --> [*] : Emergency resolved

OnDuty --> OffDuty : Shift ends
@enduml
